# UI & Component Conventions

## Stack

- **shadcn/ui** with `radix-lyra` style (`components.json`)
- **Tailwind CSS v4** — config lives in `app/globals.css`, not a separate `tailwind.config`
- **Icons**: Lucide React (`lucide-react`)
- **RSC**: enabled — prefer Server Components; add `"use client"` only when needed (hooks, events, browser APIs)

## Design tokens

Use semantic tokens from `app/globals.css`. Do not hardcode colors like `bg-zinc-50`, `text-black`, or hex values in new UI.

```tsx
// ❌ BAD
<div className="bg-zinc-50 text-black dark:bg-black">

// ✅ GOOD
<div className="bg-background text-foreground">
<Button variant="outline">Save</Button>
```

Available tokens: `background`, `foreground`, `primary`, `secondary`, `muted`, `accent`, `destructive`, `border`, `input`, `ring`, `card`, `popover`, `sidebar-*`, `chart-*`.

Dark mode uses the `.dark` class (`@custom-variant dark` in globals.css).

## Adding components

Use the shadcn CLI — do not hand-copy from docs without matching this project's style:

```bash
bunx shadcn@latest add <component>
```

New primitives go in `components/ui/`. Feature/section components go in `components/`.

## Component patterns

Follow existing `components/ui/button.tsx`:

- Use `cva` for variants; export both the component and `*Variants`
- Merge classes with `cn()` from `@/lib/utils`
- Use `@/components/ui/*` imports (see `components.json` aliases)
- Set `data-slot` on root elements (e.g. `data-slot="button"`)
- Support `asChild` via Radix `Slot.Root` when composition is needed

```tsx
import { cn } from "@/lib/utils"
import { Button } from "@/components/ui/button"

export function SaveButton({ className }: { className?: string }) {
  return (
    <Button variant="default" size="sm" className={cn(className)}>
      Save
    </Button>
  )
}
```

## Styling rules

- Use `cn()` for conditional/merged classes — never string-concatenate Tailwind classes
- Extend shadcn components via `className` prop, not by duplicating variant logic
- Use `next/image` for static images in `public/`
- Typography: body uses `font-serif` (Lora) via layout; use `font-sans` / `font-mono` only when intentional

## File layout

```
components/
  ui/          # shadcn primitives (Button, Input, …)
  *.tsx        # app-specific composed components
app/
  globals.css  # theme tokens + Tailwind imports — edit here for design system changes
  **/*.tsx     # pages and layouts
```

## Do not

- Add a legacy `tailwind.config.js` — this project uses Tailwind v4 CSS-first setup
- Edit generated shadcn files heavily — prefer wrapping in a composed component
- Use inline styles or arbitrary hex colors when a semantic token exists
- Import Radix primitives directly in pages — use `@/components/ui/*` wrappers
